NK040(thi)021:1: // byin dbang dngos grub char 'bebs bzhugs so //
NK040(thi)021:7: dbyangs ring po 'thon la 'di skad do //
NK040(thi)021:8: +aahmh'u bam gu ru ha ri ni sa badz+ra sa ma ya dza dza /
NK040(thi)021:10: yul gyi ming ni chos kyi dbyings //
NK040(thi)021:11: chos sku kun bzang yum chen la //
NK040(thi)021:12: skye med dbyings kyi mkha' 'gros bskor //
NK040(thi)021:13: gnas mchog 'di ru gshegs su gsol //
NK040(thi)021:14: bsgrub khang 'di ru byin phob cig /
NK040(thi)021:17: sgrub rdzas 'di rnams byin gyis rlobs //
NK040(thi)021:18: mar me 'di la mdangs cig stsol //
NK040(thi)021:19: zhal zas 'di la bcud cig phob //
NK040(thi)021:21: sgrub pa po la dbang bzhi bskur //
NK040(thi)021:23: yul gyi ming ni u rgyan yul //
NK040(thi)021:24: longs sku rdo rje phag mo la //
NK040(thi)021:28: yul gyi ming gi mkha' spyod gnas //
NK040(thi)021:29: sprul sku ma cig lab sgron ma //
NK040(thi)021:33: spros bral chos sku'i pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)021:34: pha gcig dam pa rgya gar la //
NK040(thi)021:35: grub thob gcod rgyud rnams kyis bskor //
NK040(thi)021:38: bde ba can gyi pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)021:39: rje btsun rigs kyi mkha' 'gros bskor //
NK040(thi)021:42: dur khrod chen po'i pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)021:43: ma cig khros ma nag mo la //
NK040(thi)021:44: dur khrod brgyad kyi mkha' 'gros bskor //
NK040(thi)021:47: chos dbyings ye shes pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)021:48: dbus phyogs sangs rgyas mkha' 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)021:49: sangs rgyas mkha' 'gro 'bum gnas mchog sogs /
NK040(thi)021:51: me long ye shes pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)021:52: shar phyogs rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)021:56: mnyam nyid ye shes pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)021:57: lho phyogs rin chen mkha' 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)021:58: rin chen mkha' 'gro 'bum gyis gnas mchog sogs /
NK040(thi)021:60: sor rtog ye shes pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)021:65: bya grub ye shes pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)021:66: byang phyogs las kyi mkha' 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)021:70: phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad steng 'og na //
NK040(thi)021:71: bzhugs pa'i sna tshogs mkha' 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)021:75: phyi rol sha za mkha' 'gro dang //
NK040(thi)021:76: zhing skyong las byed shugs 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)021:77: dam can ma sring rgya mtshos bskor //
NK040(thi)021:79: dbang bzhi bskur byin rlabs na bum thibs se theb //
NK040(thi)021:80: dngos grub char 'bebs si li li //
NK040(thi)021:81: dbu skra thor tshugs ldems se ldem //
NK040(thi)021:82: dbu rgyan dar dpyang pu ru ru //
NK040(thi)021:83: sna tshogs gar byed khyugs se khyug /
NK040(thi)021:84: mkha' 'gro'i brda skad ti ri ri //
NK040(thi)021:85: byin gyis rlabs phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK040(thi)021:86: sgrub pa po la dbang bzhi bskur //
NK040(thi)021:87: +aahmh'u bam gu ru ha ri ni sa sarba d+aak+ki
NK040(thi)021:88: ni ka ya wak+ka tsit+ta sid+d+hi pha la a we
NK040(thi)021:90: h'uh dur khrod gnas mchog nyams re dga' //
NK040(thi)021:91: tshogs brgyad gnas su dag pa'i brda //
NK040(thi)021:92: nyi zla brtsegs pa 'od re gsal //
NK040(thi)021:93: 'gags med sna tshogs shar ba'i brda //
NK040(thi)021:94: rtog med ro gdan bag re bro //
NK040(thi)021:95: snang srid mnyam nyid yum gyi thugs //
NK040(thi)021:96: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro la //
NK040(thi)021:97: bdag gis dad pas 'bul ba ni //
NK040(thi)021:98: zhing gi bla re rgyangs se rgyang //
NK040(thi)021:100: ro ras yol ba lhubs se lhub //
NK040(thi)021:102: mun sel nyi zla 'od re gsal //
NK040(thi)021:103: ma dang mkha' sha chen thang ma kad de kad //
NK040(thi)021:104: ma dang mkha' tshogs drug me tog rugs se rug /
NK040(thi)021:105: ma dang mkha' 'gro gsur chen dud pa phyu ru ru //
NK040(thi)021:107: rak+ta'i khrag mtsho me re re //
NK040(thi)021:108: ma dang 'dod yon gtor ma spungs se spung //
NK040(thi)021:110: sman chen bdud rtsi chi li li //
NK040(thi)021:111: ma dang rkang chen gling bu kyu ru ru //
NK040(thi)021:112: ma dang thod pa'i rnga chen khrabs se khrab //
NK040(thi)021:113: ma dang sba gling snyug gling kyu ru ru //
NK040(thi)021:114: ma dang mkha' 'gro gar dang brda skad sgrogs //
NK040(thi)021:115: ma dang dpa' bo'i bro brdung h'u sgra sgrogs //
NK040(thi)021:116: ma dang nam mkha' mu med gtor gzhong du //
NK040(thi)021:118: 'dzin med mchod pa bsam mi khyab //
NK040(thi)021:119: mu med mtha' yas brjod du med //
NK040(thi)021:120: nam mkha'i mtha' mnyam mchod pa 'di //
NK040(thi)021:122: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro la //
NK040(thi)021:123: phyi nang gsang gsum mchod pa 'bul //
NK040(thi)021:124: bdag cag yon mchod 'khor bcas la //
NK040(thi)021:125: tshe bsring dpal bskyed bsam pa bsgrub //
NK040(thi)021:126: lha 'dre mi gsum dbang bsdus la //
NK040(thi)021:127: zas nor dngos grub char ltar phob //
NK040(thi)021:128: bsam pa yid bzhin 'grub par mdzod //
NK040(thi)021:129: ci bsam don rnams 'grub par shog /
NK040(thi)021:130: ces mkha' 'gro rnams kyis byin brlabs sprin dpung gtib pa ltar bsam zhing /
NK040(thi)021:131: sgrub khang lha'i gzhal yas khang du byin gyis brlab bo //
